FBIS4-5929 "dreas073_c_94011" FBIS-EAS-94-073 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 North Korea Receives PRENSA LATINA Head Receives PRENSA LATINA Head SK1304121194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1124 GMT 13 Apr 94 SK1304121194 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 13 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song today received Pedro Margolles Villanueva, director general of the PRENSA LATINA of Cuba, and his companion on a visit to Korea. Present on the occasion were Vice-premier and Foreign Minister Kim Yong-nam, Director General of the Korean Central News Agency Kim Ki-yong and Cuban Ambassador E.P. to Korea Jose Ramon Rodriguez Varona. The guests warmly congratulated President Kim Il-song on his birthday and wished him a long life in good health. President Kim Il-song expressed thanks for this, conversed with the guests in a cordial and friendly atmosphere and answered questions put by the director general. President Kim Il-song arranged a luncheon for them.
